=Description=

"The purpose of the Open Micromanufacturing and Nanomanufacturing Equipment (OMNE) project is to promote innovation in the design and use of manufacturing equipment for micro-scale and nano-scale products. Particpants in the project produce Open Design equipment and machinery that is freely available via an Open Design license."
(http://www.engr.uky.edu/psl/omne/)


